column5: Hey guys  I'm taking the girlfriend and her daughter out for some shore fishing this long weekend.  I heard about belwood,puslinch, and little lake but I'm not too familiar with these lakes. Ive fished mostly simcoe and rice lake but out west I'm totally clueless. If anyone can drop me a private message to give me some sort of direction on where to start that would be greatly appreciated.
Wow I guess it's really is a secret then
Would like to thank everyone who has participated in sharing Thierry info
Hello everyone. Would like to thank everyone trying to help me out. Ended up going to Woodstock fishing for endless amount of sunfish.  Will post some pictures soon.
